{"tid":1467010,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"認錯咪得囉！聽日道歉，後日再迫爆！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:06.000Z","uid":14803,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35d242e44c9703e021d0aa9131977eff3a951539","tid":1467010,"uid":14803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:27.000Z","msg":"今晚畫面唔好睇<br />\n無論環球隻狗幫邊間做野都好，佢點都係一個記者<br />\n如果你聽日返工返學 有藍絲問起你 想挑戰你<br />\n你大方認左佢 佢反而吹你唔脹<br />\n做返場PR show<br />\n聽日入機場道個靚歉、比一日班旅客走<br />\n後日再塞爆佢老母！<br />\n<br />\n認錯 唔代表割<br />\n<br />\n記住，我地打仗打左兩個幾月 係因為集體智慧、良知、同識進化"},{"pid":"d00f0877e034dbcb51c0eedd928c17cc52de7c64","tid":1467010,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"唔道歉都講句唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c2479ed4ab7566d09e710a82f18f4d6e6936ad","tid":1467010,"uid":14803,"like":0,"disl